    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <opener> 
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">Camden</name>
                    <date when="1887-07-15">Friday Afternoon<lb/>July 15</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear friend Susan Stafford</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I should like to come down &#38; see you &#38; see George,<ptr target="n0852c"/> but I
                am quite poorly &#38; it has been such hot weather&#8212;I am quite concerned about
                him<ptr target="upa.00220_n2"/> &#38; w'd wish to help somehow&#8212;If you w'd wish a little money I can let
                you have it, as I can spare it&#8212;or if there is any thing George would like that
                I c'd get up here, you write me, &#38; it w'd be a pleasure to me to get it&#8212;I
                send George my love &#38; the same to you all&#8212;</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>Walt Whitman</signed>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
